Text: I always wants to travel the world. To find new places, meet new people and
  eat new food. See new culture and find new traditions. I always dream of visiting
  exotic places. I dont have that much resources or else, I would have travelled half
  of the world but with this opportunity at my doorstep, one can only try and hope
  to get selected
